data.description: Motivated seller due relocation. $10,000 seller contribution. This charming two-story home with a total of 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms is perfect for families seeking space and comfort. The layout of the home is practical and functional, with enough room for everyone and a versatile space that can be used as a dining room or study on the main level.     The great room opens up to the breakfast area and kitchen, which includes a work island. All of the bedrooms are located on the upper level. The Primary's suite is spacious and comes with a large bathroom featuring a glass-enclosed shower, a walk-in closet, and separate his and hers vanities. The house boasts a 2-story foyer with an overlook down below. The laundry area is conveniently located on the upper level.     This property is located in a cul-de-sac providing a peaceful and safe environment for children to play and is located near to major highways, making it easy to commute to different areas.
